---

<section
    id="contact"
    class="portfolio-slide h-screen w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-10 relative overflow-hidden bg-white/5"
>
    <div class="slide-content text-center">
        <h2
            class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold font-heading mb-8 opacity-0 scale-90"
            id="contact-title"
        >
            ¿Hablamos?
        </h2>
        <p
            class="text-xl mb-12 max-w-xl mx-auto opacity-0 scale-90"
            id="contact-description"
        >
            Siempre estoy abierto a nuevas colaboraciones y proyectos
            interesantes.
        </p>
        <div
            class="flex gap-6 justify-center opacity-0 scale-90"
            id="contact-buttons"
        >
            <a
                href="mailto:gmail@example.com"
                class="px-8 py-3 bg-primary text-background font-bold rounded-full hover:scale-105 transition-transform"
            >
                Email
            </a>
            <a
                href="/contacto"
                class="px-8 py-3 border-2 border-primary text-primary font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-primary hover:text-background transition-colors"
            >
                Contacto
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
